00:35:17,214 --> 00:35:19,123
(Video from when she was being treated)

786
00:35:19,124 --> 00:35:21,754
(She got a deep wound.)

787
00:35:21,854 --> 00:35:23,724
- Do they often bite?
- Yes.

788
00:35:23,754 --> 00:35:24,823
They're dangerous.

789
00:35:24,824 --> 00:35:26,893
(A threatening beak)

790
00:35:26,894 --> 00:35:28,463
(They always have to watch out during breeding season...)

791
00:35:28,464 --> 00:35:29,994
(as the penguins are sensitive.)

792
00:35:30,594 --> 00:35:33,364
(Don't come close while we're brooding.)

793
00:35:34,164 --> 00:35:37,404
(They enjoyed listening to the research team's stories.)

794
00:35:37,834 --> 00:35:40,674
(Emptying their bowls)

795
00:35:41,904 --> 00:35:43,543
It was warm until the very last spoonful.

796
00:35:43,544 --> 00:35:44,673
It was nice, right?

797
00:35:44,674 --> 00:35:46,543
We've brought fried rice before,

798
00:35:46,544 --> 00:35:47,913
but it got cold very quickly.

799
00:35:47,914 --> 00:35:49,313
It's tasty.

800
00:35:49,314 --> 00:35:51,514
- It's nice and warm.
- Seriously.

801
00:35:52,084 --> 00:35:54,424
We usually eat quickly and go back to work.

802
00:35:54,554 --> 00:35:55,653
It was fun to chat while eating.

803
00:35:55,654 --> 00:35:57,494
- It's easy on the stomach too.
- Exactly.

804
00:35:58,023 --> 00:35:59,358
(They prepared a thoughtful meal full of care.)

805
00:35:59,390 --> 00:36:00,565
Thank you.

806
00:36:01,324 --> 00:36:04,634
(This meal warmed up their bodies and hearts.)

807
00:36:05,064 --> 00:36:07,964
Since we're here, we want to help if we can.

808
00:36:08,034 --> 00:36:09,303
- If we can help...
- Let us know...

809
00:36:09,304 --> 00:36:11,403
if we can do anything to help.

810
00:36:11,404 --> 00:36:13,444
When we attach the location trackers,

811
00:36:13,474 --> 00:36:15,773
- Next to you.
- could you write down the data?

812
00:36:15,774 --> 00:36:17,473
- In English?
- And like in an operation room,

813
00:36:17,474 --> 00:36:19,383
when we say, "Scissors," you can hand us the scissors.

814
00:36:19,384 --> 00:36:20,813
Like an assistant?

815
00:36:20,814 --> 00:36:23,484
Just writing down the data would be very helpful.

816
00:36:23,799 --> 00:36:24,823
We can do that.

817
00:36:25,214 --> 00:36:26,424
- Okay.
- Thank you.

818
00:36:26,824 --> 00:36:28,623
- Shall we get going?
- Let's go.

819
00:36:28,624 --> 00:36:30,554
- Thank you for the meal.
- No problem.
